    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem and it is truly in showroom condition\u2014honestly, it still feels brand new! I've babied this car from day one; it\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and drives like a total dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a flawless car that looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
