      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in concourse condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically pristine with a proactive Double VANOS overhaul and documented subframe reinforcement already completed. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with an M-Variable Lock differential for optimal corner-exit power delivery. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the chassis remains rigid with zero oxidation or suspension bushing fatigue. A turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
