      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, so it\u2019s in absolute pristine condition with zero issues. It drives like a dream and still has that 'new car' magic. I'm looking for a smooth sale for someone who will love it as much as I have. Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look! \u2728",
